Route 9 -- Borland Road NW

Central western Orange County

Date -- July 27, 2003
Time -- 5:32 EDT
Observers -- Haven and Minna Wiley

NOTES

Despite the late date (this was a make-up for a route missed earlier), lots of birds sang.
Also lots of owls called at dawn.
